Siggy !

68
00:05:27,013 --> 00:05:28,846
Siggy !
/ Kubilang, mana anak - anakku ?

69
00:05:29,566 --> 00:05:30,782
Siggy !

70
00:05:32,435 --> 00:05:33,936
Rollo. Rollo.

71
00:05:33,937 --> 00:05:35,804
Mana, Siggy ? Aku tak bisa temukan dia.
/ Rollo ! Rollo...,

72
00:05:35,805 --> 00:05:37,238
Siggy sudah mati.

73
00:05:42,579 --> 00:05:43,579
Bagaimana bisa ?

74
00:05:45,882 --> 00:05:48,900
Ubbe dan Hvitserk jatuh
ke dalam danau beku.

75
00:05:49,819 --> 00:05:52,503
Siggy menyelamatkan nyawa
mereka, tapi dia tenggelam.

76
00:05:53,656 --> 00:05:55,573
