/ Aku bukan menanyaimu, Helga.

90
00:07:01,191 --> 00:07:02,557
Aku bertanya padamu.

91
00:07:04,727 --> 00:07:05,944
Helga benar.

92
00:07:05,945 --> 00:07:08,663
Kami bertiga bergantian
menjaga anak - anak kita.

93
00:07:09,999 --> 00:07:11,683
Kurasa itu lucu...

94
00:07:11,684 --> 00:07:14,235
