Kita semua kehilangan seseorang !

112
00:08:24,307 --> 00:08:28,092
Saudara, sepupu, teman.

113
00:08:28,311 --> 00:08:30,011
Apa istimewanya kehilanganmu ?

114
00:08:32,282 --> 00:08:34,682
Sebaiknya kau jangan
main - main denganku !

115
00:08:35,551 --> 00:08:38,286
