213
00:17:23,360 --> 00:17:24,442
Kalf.

214
00:17:26,713 --> 00:17:27,729
Kalf.

215
00:17:30,517 --> 00:17:33,451
Tak mungkin.
/ Tapi itu telah terjadi.

216
00:17:33,870 --> 00:17:36,788
Kalf menjadikan dirinya
Earl baru di Hedeby.

217
00:17:38,708 --> 00:17:41,560
Kubantu kau di Wessex,
sekarang kau harus bantu aku.

218
00:17:41,561 --> 00:17:43,963
Bersama, kita bisa gulingkan
si tukang rampas ini.

219
00:17:43,964 --> 00:17:47,548
Pertama, kau ikut ke Wessex
atas kemauan sendiri.

220
00:17:47,834 --> 00:17:50,034
Kedua, jika ada perang saudara...,

221
00:17:50,871 --> 00:17:53,538
...banyak orang kita
yang akan mati.

222
00:17:54,975 --> 00:17:57,409
Apa takhtamu sungguh
sepenting itu bagimu ?

223
00:17:57,410 --> 00:17:58,928
Ya.
/ Kenapa ?

224
00:17:58,929 --> 00:18:02,063
Karena itu hak sahku !

225
